dmca.title: Electronics vendor claims its photos were copied
dmca.body:
I am filling this DMCA report regarding the matter of copyright infringement.

It has come to my attention that MCS machine control services, Inc. The owner of

www.fanuc.net 
www.cncparts.net 
www.fanucparts.com

Which operates out of Texas, USA. Has been infringing our rights of ownership and copyright over 2 different photographs that it persists to place on its websites. I have approached the owner of the sites, [Private] (MCS owner) and asked him politely to remove the photos
